comments.body: `CAmount`s are not floats; just use `1`. Since you're not using it elsewhere you may want to just do `setValue(1)` below.
You may wanna use `CURRENCY_UNIT` instead of hard-coded `BTC` here. It's defined in `policy/feerate.h`.
